FBIS4-7329 "dreas083_g_94007" FBIS-EAS-94-083 Daily Report 27 Apr 1994 SOUTHEAST ASIA Burma Official Appointments Announced by SLORC Official Appointments Announced by SLORC Deputy Ministers Appointed BK2704143994 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 27 Apr 94 BK2704143994 Rangoon Radio Burma Burmese BFN [Notification No. 23/94 of the State Law and Order Restoration Council; issued on 27 April] [Text] Appointment of deputy ministers; The State Law and Order Restoration Council [SLORC] has appointed the following persons deputy ministers of the respective ministries; 1. Dr. Than Nyunt, Ministry of Education 2. U Aung Thein, Ministry of Livestock Breeding and Fisheries 3. Colonel Aung San, Ministry of Construction By the authority vested in me, Signed; Khin Nyunt, lieutenant general, secretary-1 of the SLORC.
